@page
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
            <h1 class="display-4 text-center mb-4">About CampusConnect</h1>
            <p class="lead text-center mb-5">
                CampusConnect is dedicated to bridging the gap between students, universities, and employers, creating a seamless pathway from education to career.
            </p>

            <div class="mb-5">
                <h2 class="h3 mb-3">Our Mission</h2>
                <p>Our mission is to democratize access to opportunity and help every student build a fulfilling career, regardless of their background or where they go to school. We strive to empower students with the tools and connections they need to explore their potential and launch their professional lives successfully.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="row mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h3 class="h4 mb-3">For Students</h3>
                    <p>Discover exciting job and internship opportunities from a diverse range of employers. Build your profile, connect with recruiters, and get a head start on your career journey. CampusConnect provides resources, insights, and a network to help you find the right fit.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h3 class="h4 mb-3">For Employers</h3>
                    <p>Connect with a vast pool of talented and motivated students from universities across the nation. Our platform makes it easy to find the right candidates for your internships, entry-level positions, and experienced roles, streamlining your recruitment process.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h3 class="h4 mb-3">For Universities</h3>
                    <p>Partner with CampusConnect to enhance your career services and provide your students with unparalleled access to employers and job opportunities. We offer tools to manage career fairs, track student engagement, and improve graduate outcomes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-5">
                <h2 class="h3 mb-3">Our Vision</h2>
                <p>We envision a world where every student has the support and resources to achieve their career aspirations. CampusConnect is committed to building a future where talent is recognized and nurtured, and where meaningful connections lead to impactful careers. We are constantly innovating to make the journey from campus to career smoother and more equitable for everyone involved.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center">
                <p><strong>Join us in shaping the future of career development.</strong></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>